06:23.293 --> 06:24.527
Who else was here?

06:24.529 --> 06:26.863
No one who lives here.
Family was gone at the time.

06:26.865 --> 06:28.197
Somebody was here.

06:28.199 --> 06:29.432
Nobody pours a second drink

06:29.434 --> 06:32.268
when their first drink's
sitting two feet away.

06:33.504 --> 06:37.273
I'm not feeling natural causes.

06:43.067 --> 06:49.967
